data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Beautiful one story house with gorgeous water view!   Spacious Split plan. Features: large open kitchen with island, closet pantry, all kitchen appliances included, Formal living and dining, walk in closets, indoor, laundry with sink, 24x24 marble tiles through out, & 2 car garage with opener. Community features: Resort like style living, guard gated, community pools, fitness center, tennis, basketball, & volleyball courts, conservation lots, access to lake toho, & more. Rent includes basic cable, internet and irrigation.
